headline: Otis STEM Program Propels Student Alum to an International Scholarship
summary: NORTHAMPTON, MA / ACCESS Newswire / June 2, 2025 / Pannawish Tanthawichian was a participating high school student in the Otis Made to Move Communities™ challenge in 2022-23. Now he's leaving his home in Thailand with a scholarship to study computer ...
